---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTA from '../components/ui/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Website Design – Sites That Convert | Bluebird"
	description="Professional, responsive small business websites built for conversion. Mobile-first, fast, and SEO-ready. Clear process, 4–8 week delivery, ongoing support."
	canonicalURL="/website-design"
	keywords="website design, small business website, responsive web design, conversion-focused website, local business website, Bluebird"
>
	<section class="relative pt-28 sm:pt-32 md:pt-36 pb-20 sm:pb-24 md:pb-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bg overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-accent/3 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
		<div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<header class="mb-12 sm:mb-16">
				<h1 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
					Website design
				</h1>
				<p class="font-body text-lg text-textMuted max-w-2xl">
					Websites designed to convert local prospects. We build professional, responsive small business sites that turn visitors into customers—fast load times, clear calls-to-action, and built for findability in your market.
				</p>
			</header>

			<!-- Features (inspired by LocalSite value props, tailored to Bluebird) -->
			<h2 class="font-headline text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-6">What you get</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/30 p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accentSubtle flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Responsive & mobile-friendly</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">Every site we build is mobile-first. It looks and works great on phones, tablets, and desktops—so you don’t lose leads on small screens.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/30 p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accentSubtle flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Conversion-optimized</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">We place calls-to-action where they make sense—when someone is ready to contact you or book. No guesswork; we design for the outcome you want.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/30 p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accentSubtle flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Search-engine friendly</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">Clean structure, fast loading, and basics done right so Google can crawl and rank your site. Pair with our Local SEO when you’re ready to get found.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Built for you / changes that reflect your needs -->
			<div class="rounded-2xl bg-accent/5 border border-accent/10 p-6 sm:p-8 mb-12">
				<h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Built for your business</h2>
				<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-4">
					Your site should reflect how good your business is. We work with you on structure and content so the result fits your brand and your audience—no template dump. You get a clear process, a realistic timeline (most projects in 4–8 weeks), and a site you’re proud to send people to.
				</p>
				<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
					We use modern tech (HTML, CSS, and a lean stack) so your site stays fast and maintainable. As standards change, we keep things compliant and up to date—and we’re here after launch for updates, tweaks, and optional Local SEO so you keep converting.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- FAQ-style -->
			<div class="rounded-2xl bg-accent/5 border border-accent/10 p-6 sm:p-8 mb-12">
				<h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Common questions</h2>
				<details class="group border-b border-accentSubtle/30 pb-4 mb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0 last:mb-0">
					<summary class="font-body text-base font-medium text-text cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
						How long does a website take?
						<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-textMuted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
					</summary>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 leading-relaxed">
						Most projects launch in 4–8 weeks. We align on scope and content first, then design and build in clear phases. No endless revisions—we keep the process tight so you get a live site without the wait.
					</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-accentSubtle/30 pb-4 mb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0 last:mb-0">
					<summary class="font-body text-base font-medium text-text cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
						Do you only do small business sites?
						<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-textMuted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
					</summary>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 leading-relaxed">
						We focus on websites and web apps for small and mid-size businesses—local services, professional practices, and brands that want a clear, conversion-focused presence. If you need a custom app or something more complex, we do that too; just tell us what you’re after.
					</p>
				</details>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<p class="font-body text-sm text-textMuted mb-4">Ready for a site that converts? Tell us about your business and we’ll outline options and next steps.</p>
				<CTA href="/contact" variant="primary" size="md" showArrow={true}>
					Get in touch
				</CTA>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
